Interface LocalizedNamedObject

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    NamedEntity<T>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface LocalizedNamedObject
    Interface for Objects that have localized names and optionally also descriptions.
    Author:
    Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com), Ken Logan (ken@i2rd.com)

    • Method Detail

      • getDescription

        LocalizedObjectKey getDescription()
        Get the description of the object.
        Returns:

      • getName

        LocalizedObjectKey getName()
        Get the name of the object.
        Returns:
        the key representing the name of the object. Usually this won't be null for a properly configured object.
